<H1>Guidelines for creating a password</H1>

<H2>Don't</H2>

<UL>
<LI>choose a word from a dictionary</LI>
<LI>use personal information such as your name, make
of car etc.</LI>
<LI>tell anyone your password</LI>
<LI>write your password down anywhere</LI>
<LI>use the password you were given when you first got your
account on the system</LI>
</UL>

<H2>Do</H2>
<UL>
<LI>choose an obscure password preferably between 6
and 8 characters in length, of mixed case and
containing at least one non-alphanumeric character
such as ! or @</LI>
<LI>change your password at regular intervals</LI>
</UL>

